Requirements
============

Python 2.[67].*

Release Process
===============

http://code.aashedev.org/stars/wiki/ReleaseProcess

Fabric
======

This project uses fabric to deploy code to dev, stage, and production environments

Example Deploy
--------------

>$ bin/fab <name> deploy
You will be prompted to offer a specific branch/tag, otherwise the latest default branch will be deployed...

Current configuration are:

* vagrant
* starsapp01

Vagrant
=======

Vagrant is a tool to generate a virtual machines on your local box. Right now it's configured to bring up one instance:

* web1: 33.33.33.10

>$ cd vagrant
>$ vagrant up

web1
----

Configured with the following:

* stars application paths (/var/www/stars/)
* apache w/ mod_wsgi
* nginx
* rabbitmq
* django-celery
* memcached
* python

Complete deploy
---------------

>$ cd ..
>$ bin/fab vagrant deploy

Site up at: http://33.33.33.10